Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Walk Into the Light"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your anger and hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take in the darkness of heart within this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay back, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With my way of justice and beliefs on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just {\i1}waiting{\i0} for you to use the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if things keep going this way, I'm bound to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, this is {\i0}my{\i1} battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One that bets my\N way of justice and my beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, the day will come when the two of us must part ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A time will come when the both of us will have to fight a difficult battle on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that time is right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other... Me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the one who chose this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the mission that has been passed along to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is both mine\N and everyone else's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My other self...  No matter how much it hurts, please don't waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in the strength of our bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your friends and the Monsters who believe in you are always by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we're separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... always... by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}PARTNER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let myself be consumed by the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because within me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I've... paid you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step over my corpse... and go forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What point is there in suffering so much by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are nothing more than a cursed soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just raise my hand, that fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Put an end to all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring your existence back to nil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... nil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I used to be nil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply trapped within the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Null, from the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I lose them, I have nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I have to vanish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing... left within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Past memories... My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does someone like me who holds no existence have it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something in my heart that can never be erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see... I never noticed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deep within my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Among the bonds I've woven with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a vessel of memories....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is my everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am not nil...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I still have the vessel inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how many times it takes... I can still be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My memories with everyone deep within me can never be erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The vessel of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The darkness of heart in this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using the vessel I hold within myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hereby erase you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tsunami... dissipated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a miracle just occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gone...! It disappeared, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... such a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the malice you've carried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nameless Pharaoh has taken it all away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For saving my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you two must return to your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new future is awaiting you all beyond that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kris!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father. It is also time for us to cross over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother is waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Let's get ready to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, where's Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, we gotta get out of here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, everyone! Get on the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell're you doing, Honda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what happens to Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do for now is believe Yugi's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last thing I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! The hell you doin' here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you! Why're {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ya see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}-I don't know how my soul came back...\N -Don't know how my soul came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-But Yugi!\N -But Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-I won't forgive you!\N -Freakin' unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'm gonna beat you for sure next time!\N -I'm gonna beat ya for sure next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humph! And what exactly is that piece of garbage supposed to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...memento of my little brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My little brother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...killed by your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You couldn't {\i0}save{\i1} him. Your little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What... a-are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You still don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You couldn't manage to save your younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}You're{\i1} the loser\N based on this point alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda... If that had been\N me instead of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would not have let my little brother die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter {\i0}what{\i1} it took!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amelda! Witness the power of a True Duelist and the splendor of the Chosen Ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tyrant Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not bad, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miruko... I'm going to live as much as I can for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shaking...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I actually {\i1}afraid{\i0} of the bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've felt like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now! Let's get on with it, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burning Knuckle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Bang Dragon Blow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi, I leave Mai to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}VARON!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you left, Mai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a stupid man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dueling is not meant to fight for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fighting is to win for yourself. \NAren't you the one who said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon did his best as a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's you, I won't allow anyone to belittle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I fought seriously with Varon, I understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While Dueling with him, we started to understand each other as we spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me too. I want to feel what you're feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why, Mai, I will fight you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, my feelings will reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me too. I want to receive your true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You win... Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During your battle with Varon, you were already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to see your face anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Duel... was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... No! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that winning wouldn't change a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That even if you win...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will become a Duelist worthy of the both of you and I'll return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were we saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both my Masters, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now both the Duel Monsters Realm and your world have been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Orichalcos has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the hatred filling its soul has been destroyed, we're going to try letting it live among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it will realize how wonderful the world of Duel Monsters is once it lives with us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our grudge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who owes you my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have your strength, I wouldn't have been able to overcome the darkness in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? The aurora appeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl and the Legendary Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're returning to the Duel Monsters World.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hermos card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph... Was it all a dream in the end...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps just an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God they're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little squirt, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get outta here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya don't hurry, we're takin' off without ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, arrogant as always, the idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happens as soon as he learns Yugi's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What Black Magician Girl was about to say before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That the curse of this planet is sealed deep within my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if the other me were to control the darkness in his heart once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that curse could be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no need for me to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because my other self is much different than how he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has now overcome the darkness of his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and is about to walk into a new light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he's been reborn as a true Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle against Doma has finally come to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we managed to protect the world somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thinking back on things, it's been a tough battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Yugi! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to go back to America,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's just relax for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... have no way of returning home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The KC Grand Prix Opening Game"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
